OL,3,CMark Drakeford says 'scars' of 1984
OL,4,Cminers' strike 'live on' 40 years later
OL,6,FFirst Minister says the scars of the
OL,7,F1984-85 miners' strike "live on" in
OL,8,FWales 40 years later.
OL,10,FThe strike, which lasted three days
OL,11,Fshort of a year, began on 6 March 1984.
OL,13,FMr Drakeford said: "I think we're
OL,14,Fstill dealing with the legacy of it in
OL,15,Fa whole series of ways.
OL,17,F"It was such a traumatic experience
OL,18,Ffor Wales that it continues to echo
OL,19,Fdown the years in terms of people's
OL,20,Fmemories of it, the shaping impact it
OL,21,Fhad on people's views of the world."
