OL,3,CMark Drakeford says 'scars' of 1984
OL,4,Cminers' strike 'live on' 40 years later
OL,6,FHe says Wales is still recovering from
OL,7,Fthe end of heavy industry, which he
OL,8,Fsays came to an end in "the absolute
OL,9,Fopposite way that we talk about today,
OL,10,F'a just transition'.
OL,12,F"The way the industry in Wales came to
OL,13,Fend was brutal, and that continues to
OL,14,Fleave its legacy."
