OL,3,CMark Drakeford says 'scars' of 1984
OL,4,Cminers' strike 'live on' 40 years later
OL,6,FAlthough he acknowledged that "coal
OL,7,Fmining was coming to an end", he said
OL,8,Fit "ought to have come to an end in a
OL,9,Fway that was managed, that was
OL,10,Fsympathetic to those communities, and
OL,11,Fthat created new opportunities
OL,12,Falongside the opportunities that were
OL,13,Fdiminishing.
OL,15,F"None of that happened."
