OL,4,Cminers' strike 'live on' 40 years later
OL,6,F"But I don't think people fell out
OL,7,Fover trivial things, they fell out
OL,8,Fover the most profound challenges that
OL,9,Fthose communities were facing."
OL,11,FYou can watch ITV Wales' special Wales
OL,12,Fat Six programme on the 40th
OL,13,Fanniversary of the 1984 miners' strike
OL,14,Fat 6pm on Monday 4 March.
